{
  "chapter": 40,
  "chapter_summary": "本章写鸠摩智在少林与虚竹激斗，虚竹以粗浅少林招式、逍遥派内力和天山武学逐渐扭转危局，鸠摩智偷学小无相功缺失第七册的隐患亦被逼显。梅兰竹菊四剑乔装入寺护主，令虚竹破戒与身兼灵鹫宫主之事败露，玄慈、玄寂等当众议定依戒律将虚竹逐出少林并责罚其师。随后各路豪杰因丐帮新帮主庄聚贤广撒英雄帖齐至少林，段正淳、段誉、四大恶人及慕容复一线相继牵入。章末追述慕容复一行救得丐帮伤者易大彪，获知西夏银川公主招亲榜文，慕容复遂把此视为复国外援契机，欲先赴少林观局。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "韦陀掌",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 6,
      "line_end": 6
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "一空到底",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 10,
      "line_end": 10
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "料想这一掌开碑裂石，已将他肩骨击成碎片。那知虚竹有",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 22,
      "line_end": 22
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "护体，但觉肩头一阵疼痛，便即猱身复上，双掌自左向右划下，这招",
      "tone": "痛苦",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 22,
      "line_end": 22
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "燃木刀法",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 32,
      "line_end": 32
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "燃木刀法",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 36,
      "line_end": 36
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "一想到此节，出招便只攻击虚竹面门，",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 44,
      "line_end": 44
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "韦陀掌",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 46,
      "line_end": 46
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "但虚竹用以应付的，却只一路",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 50,
      "line_end": 50
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "，且在对方迅若闪电的急攻之下，心中手上全无变招的余裕，打出一招",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 50,
      "line_end": 50
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "，又是一招",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 50,
      "line_end": 50
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "，来来去去，便只依样葫芦的一招",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 50,
      "line_end": 50
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "臂臑穴",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 54,
      "line_end": 54
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "还施水阁",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 60,
      "line_end": 60
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "舅太太",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 78,
      "line_end": 78
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "阿朱、阿碧两个鬼丫头呢，死到那里去了？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 82,
      "line_end": 82
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "又问：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 84,
      "line_end": 84
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "琅嬛玉洞",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 112,
      "line_end": 112
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "琅嬛",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 114,
      "line_end": 114
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "见他走到一只柜子前，柜门上横排",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 120,
      "line_end": 120
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "四字，下面竖行两行字，刻着",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 120,
      "line_end": 120
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "八个字，乃用绿色颜料填色，心想：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 120,
      "line_end": 120
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "那老人长长呼了口气，双手捧肚，这才答道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 134,
      "line_end": 134
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "鸠摩智听到",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 146,
      "line_end": 146
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "王夫人在那老人身畔的一张椅上坐下，说道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 150,
      "line_end": 150
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "那老人摇摇头，说道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 154,
      "line_end": 154
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "爹，是你动的手，是不是？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 158,
      "line_end": 158
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "王夫人道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 160,
      "line_end": 160
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "那老人摇头道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 162,
      "line_end": 162
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "琅嬛玉洞",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 176,
      "line_end": 176
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "王夫人读道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 200,
      "line_end": 200
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "王夫人读道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 202,
      "line_end": 202
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "琅嬛玉洞",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 212,
      "line_end": 212
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "于是打开",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 216,
      "line_end": 216
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "某月某日，收银几钱几分，购猪心猪肺几副",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 236,
      "line_end": 236
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "无滞、无碍",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 242,
      "line_end": 242
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "无分别境界",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 242,
      "line_end": 242
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "刚柔功法不能同练",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 256,
      "line_end": 256
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "天耳通",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 258,
      "line_end": 258
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "小无相",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 268,
      "line_end": 268
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "龙爪功",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 272,
      "line_end": 272
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不要脸的东西，快快投降！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 356,
      "line_end": 356
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "休伤他性命！",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 360,
      "line_end": 360
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "如此有扰了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 388,
      "line_end": 388
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "众位师兄，请！",
      "tone": "恳求",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 394,
      "line_end": 394
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "兰剑道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 402,
      "line_end": 402
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "随即在如来佛像前跪倒，说道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 408,
      "line_end": 408
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "竹剑指着玄慈道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 414,
      "line_end": 414
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "虚竹暗暗叫苦：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 448,
      "line_end": 448
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "又听兰剑笑道：",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 450,
      "line_end": 450
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "是！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 460,
      "line_end": 460
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我们偏偏要妄言妄动，你管得着么？",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 464,
      "line_end": 464
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "僧袍微扬，双手隔着衣袖分拿四女手腕。玄惭使的是",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 466,
      "line_end": 466
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "，玄愧使的是",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 466,
      "line_end": 466
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "，玄念使的是",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 466,
      "line_end": 466
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "，玄净使的则是",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 466,
      "line_end": 466
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "抛剑，抛剑！不可动手！",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 472,
      "line_end": 472
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "兰剑叫道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 478,
      "line_end": 478
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "抓住她手腕的玄愧大师须眉皆白，已七十来岁年纪，她却呼之为",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 478,
      "line_end": 478
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你再不放手，我可要骂你老婆了。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 480,
      "line_end": 480
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "一口唾液，向玄净喷去。玄净侧头让过，手指加劲，菊剑只痛得",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 482,
      "line_end": 482
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "虚竹，你将经过情由，从头说来，休得稍有隐瞒。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 490,
      "line_end": 490
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "是。弟子诚心禀告。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 492,
      "line_end": 492
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "他这么说，竟是要驱逐虚竹出寺。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 552,
      "line_end": 552
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "放下屠刀，立地成佛",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 570,
      "line_end": 570
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "苦海无边，回头是岸",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 570,
      "line_end": 570
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "顿悟",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 572,
      "line_end": 572
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "玄渡道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 588,
      "line_end": 588
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "他一提到四僧，众僧一齐合什念佛：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 598,
      "line_end": 598
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "大韦陀杵",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 602,
      "line_end": 602
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "以彼之道，还施彼身",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 604,
      "line_end": 604
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "大韦陀杵",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 606,
      "line_end": 606
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "以方丈之见，却是如何？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 616,
      "line_end": 616
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "方丈高见，愿遵法旨。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 626,
      "line_end": 626
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "师弟，请你执行本寺戒律。",
      "tone": "恳求",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 628,
      "line_end": 628
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "转头向知客僧侣道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 630,
      "line_end": 630
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "以命护教，以身殉寺",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 636,
      "line_end": 636
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "灵鹫宫",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 664,
      "line_end": 664
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "既然如此，外人不便多所置喙了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 668,
      "line_end": 668
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "虚竹道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 672,
      "line_end": 672
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "虚竹听说只罚打他一百棍子，衡之自己所犯四大戒律，实在一点也不算重，忙道：",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 680,
      "line_end": 680
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "玄寂又道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 682,
      "line_end": 682
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "韦陀掌",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 690,
      "line_end": 690
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "观心、觉贤、道清等高僧心中却连呼：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 696,
      "line_end": 696
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "方丈师伯祖教诲，弟子不敢忘记。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 726,
      "line_end": 726
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "慧轮听者。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 728,
      "line_end": 728
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "慧轮颤声道：",
      "tone": "颤声",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 734,
      "line_end": 734
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "师叔祖，弟子愿代师父领受三十杖责。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 736,
      "line_end": 736
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "又道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 756,
      "line_end": 756
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "一个阴声细气的声音说道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 772,
      "line_end": 772
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "群豪都道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 778,
      "line_end": 778
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "诸葛中老脸胀得通红，连连解释：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 816,
      "line_end": 816
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "玄生哼了一声，道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 818,
      "line_end": 818
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "诸葛中道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 820,
      "line_end": 820
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "大韦陀杵",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 840,
      "line_end": 840
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "犬子段誉得蒙明王垂青，携之东来，听犬子言道，一路上多聆教诲，大有进益，段某感激不尽，这里谢过。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 846,
      "line_end": 846
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不敢！段公子怎么不随殿下前来？",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 846,
      "line_end": 846
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "犬子不知去了何处？说不定又落入了奸人恶僧之手，正要向国师请教。",
      "tone": "恳求",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 846,
      "line_end": 846
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "段公子的下落，小僧倒也知道。唉！可惜啊可惜！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 846,
      "line_end": 846
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "便道：",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 865,
      "line_end": 865
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "跟着长叹一声，道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 873,
      "line_end": 873
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "他见段正淳又即脸上变色，这才微微一笑，说道：",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 875,
      "line_end": 875
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "家学渊源，将门虎子",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 893,
      "line_end": 893
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这不肖孩子⋯⋯",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 895,
      "line_end": 895
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "段正淳知他是讥讽自己风流放荡，也不以为忤，续道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 897,
      "line_end": 897
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "鸠摩智摇头道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 899,
      "line_end": 899
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "段正淳还了一礼，心下甚奇，见他形貌打扮，是少林寺中一个小辈僧人，却不知如何称段誉为",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 907,
      "line_end": 907
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "，问道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 907,
      "line_end": 907
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "那青年僧人便是虚竹，说道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 909,
      "line_end": 909
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "凌波微步",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 915,
      "line_end": 915
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "形销骨立、面黄肌瘦、死活难知",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 917,
      "line_end": 917
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "二哥，你又做和尚了？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 919,
      "line_end": 919
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "梦中姑娘",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 921,
      "line_end": 921
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "姑苏慕容",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 927,
      "line_end": 927
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "仰天打个哈哈，正想说几句话遮掩，忽听得门外一个阴恻恻的声音说道：",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 937,
      "line_end": 937
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "恶贯满盈",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 941,
      "line_end": 941
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "无恶不作",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 943,
      "line_end": 943
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "凶神恶煞",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 943,
      "line_end": 943
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "穷凶极恶",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 943,
      "line_end": 943
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "南海鳄神听他叫出",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 955,
      "line_end": 955
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "三字，那是逃不脱的了，恶狠狠的道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 955,
      "line_end": 955
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "段誉叫声：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 961,
      "line_end": 961
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "拔出单刀，循气息急奔过去，心想：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 971,
      "line_end": 971
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "糟糕，来迟了一步。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 975,
      "line_end": 975
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "邓百川道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 981,
      "line_end": 981
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "公冶干道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 981,
      "line_end": 981
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "老兄，你这还没死透吗？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 987,
      "line_end": 987
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "风波恶道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 995,
      "line_end": 995
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "那老丐摇了摇头，说道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 995,
      "line_end": 995
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "风波恶、包不同等都",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 995,
      "line_end": 995
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "包不同道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 1001,
      "line_end": 1001
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "那老丐道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 1005,
      "line_end": 1005
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "原来如此。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 1017,
      "line_end": 1017
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "那老丐连连点头，道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 1027,
      "line_end": 1027
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "慕容复问道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 1027,
      "line_end": 1027
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "那老丐气愤愤的道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 1029,
      "line_end": 1029
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "便是那铁头怪人？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 1031,
      "line_end": 1031
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "那老丐道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 1039,
      "line_end": 1039
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "说着伸手要到怀中去掏摸什么东西，却力不从心，道：",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 1039,
      "line_end": 1039
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "公冶干猜到他心意，问道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 1039,
      "line_end": 1039
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "连说了三个",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 1055,
      "line_end": 1055
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "慕容复道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 1059,
      "line_end": 1059
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你⋯⋯你是本帮的大仇人⋯⋯",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 1063,
      "line_end": 1063
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "邓百川皱眉道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 1089,
      "line_end": 1089
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "公冶干道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 1091,
      "line_end": 1091
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "非也，非也！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 1097,
      "line_end": 1097
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "包不同道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 1099,
      "line_end": 1099
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "非也，非也！我瞧你说话之时嘴角含笑，其意不诚⋯⋯",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 1113,
      "line_end": 1113
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "包不同道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 1115,
      "line_end": 1115
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我的想法，和三弟大大不同。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 1121,
      "line_end": 1121
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "公冶干笑道：",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 1125,
      "line_end": 1125
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "二哥，到底你以为如何？",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 1127,
      "line_end": 1127
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "当今之世，大辽、大宋、吐蕃、西夏、大理五国并峙，除了大理一国僻处南疆，与世无争之外，其余四国，都有混一宇内、并吞天下之志⋯⋯",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 1127,
      "line_end": 1127
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "重建大燕",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 1141,
      "line_end": 1141
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "斗转星移",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 1143,
      "line_end": 1143
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "以彼之道，还施彼身",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 1151,
      "line_end": 1151
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "公冶干道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 1183,
      "line_end": 1183
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "包不同哈哈一笑，说道：",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 1189,
      "line_end": 1189
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "邓百川笑道：",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 1191,
      "line_end": 1191
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "随即正色道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 1193,
      "line_end": 1193
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
